{
    "text": "Hallgr\u00edmskirkja the heart of Reykjavik, is a Lutheran (Church of Iceland) parish church in Reykjav\u00edk, Iceland. At 74.5 metres (244 ft) tall, it is the largest church in Iceland and among the tallest structures in the country. Have you seen it before?  Credits to the talented: 1. @agnieszkamrowka.photography  2. @_robertorinaldi_ 3. @pebuyck 4. @leonardopicollo \u2022 \u2022 #wheniniceland #Reykjavik #iceland.explore #artofvisuals #guidetoiceland #lostiniceland #jaw_dropping_shots #ig_auroraborealis #ig_iceland #nature_perfection #nightphotography #naturelover_gr #earthpix #earthofficial #bevisuallyinspired #sonyalpha #longexposure_shots #ig_shotz #nightphotography_exclusive #wolrdtravelcaptures #offtoiceland #Hot_shotz #iceland  #longexpoelite #beyondthelands_ #depthsofearth #icelandair #master_shots #Fantastic_earth #nightviewplanet",
